    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $f(x) = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\pi}}\\mathrm{e}^{-x^2 +2x - 1} = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2\\pi}\\cdot\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}}}\\mathrm{e}^{-\\frac{(x - 1)^2}{2\\left(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}}\\right)^2}},$ 得 $X\\sim N\\left(1,\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$ ",
