        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} E (X) = \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {+ \\infty} x f (x) d x = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {\\pi}} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {+ \\infty} x e ^ {- (x - 1) ^ {2}} d x \\\\ = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {\\pi}} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {+ \\infty} [ 1 + (x - 1) ] e ^ {- (x - 1) ^ {2}} d (x - 1) = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {\\pi}} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {+ \\infty} (1 + x) e ^ {- x ^ {2}} d x \\\\ = \\frac {2}{\\sqrt {\\pi}} \\int_ {0} ^ {+ \\infty} e ^ {- x ^ {2}} d x \\xlongequal {x ^ {2} = t} \\frac {2}{\\sqrt {\\pi}} \\int_ {0} ^ {+ \\infty} \\frac {1}{2 \\sqrt {t}} e ^ {- t} d t = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {\\pi}} \\int_ {0} ^ {+ \\infty} t ^ {- \\frac {1}{2}} e ^ {- t} d t = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {\\pi}} \\Gamma \\left(\\frac {1}{2}\\right) = 1. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
