        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $F_{Z}(z) = P\\{Z \\leqslant z\\} = P\\{2X + Y \\leqslant z\\} = \\iint_{2x + y \\leqslant z} f(x, y) \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y,$ ",
