        "text": "当 $0 \\leqslant z < 2$ 时， $F_{Z}(z) = \\int_{0}^{\\frac{z}{2}} \\mathrm{d}x \\int_{0}^{z - 2x} \\mathrm{e}^{-y} \\mathrm{d}y = \\int_{0}^{\\frac{z}{2}} (1 - \\mathrm{e}^{2x - z}) \\mathrm{d}x = \\frac{z}{2} - \\frac{1}{2} + \\frac{1}{2} \\mathrm{e}^{-z}$ ;",
